Package: ipv
Type: Package
Title: Computation of housing price indices
Version: 0.1.5
Author: F. Tusell
Maintainer: F. Tusell <fernando.tusell@ehu.es>
Description: Computation of price indices from information in the web portal idealista.com and bail data.
    The implementation is geared towards a particular application and sources of information, but we have attempted to write functions in a way that make their adaptation to other settings feasible.
